Write a C program to read “n” value and display following pattern

#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
    int n,i,j;
    printf("Enter the n value: ");
    scanf("%d",&n);
    for(i=n;i>=1;i--)
   {
      for(j=n;j>=i;j--)
      {
         printf("%d ",j);
      }
      printf("\n");
   }

    return 0;
}

INPUT AND OUTPUT:

Enter the n value: 6
6 
6 5 
6 5 4 
6 5 4 3 
6 5 4 3 2 
6 5 4 3 2 1 
